'''Dag''' can mean several things:

* In mathematics, '''Dag''' or '''DAG''' is an abbreviation for a [[directed acyclic graph]].
* In [[Norse mythology]], ''Dag'' is an [[Old Norse orthography|anglicized]] form of [[Dagr]].
* In [[Biology]], DAG is an acronym for Diacylglycerol, a second messenger of G-proteins that activates protein kinase C.

See also [[DAG]].

